lead_paragraph: Wayne Rooney can help ease the pressure on beleaguered Manchester United manager Louis van Gaal and move closer to Bobby Charlton's club scoring record if he maintains his hot streak against Stoke City in the Premier League on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: In-Form Rooney Seeks to Keep Heat Off Van Gaal
